{"name":"Greataxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-double-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The classic barbarian axe, but which also includes more historical versions such as the bardiche, voulge, or Dane axe. The greataxe has incredible potential for damage, and the master greataxe wielder fells even the stoutest of foes with reliability not seen in many other weapon styles.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"RME","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":30,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d12+@mod",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"axes","baseItem":"greataxe","properties":{"unt":false,"bsc":true,"mst":false,"aff":false,"amm":false,"awk":false,"bar":false,"bal":false,"bra":false,"con":false,"def":false,"dis":true,"dbl":false,"ent":false,"fir":false,"fin":false,"hip":false,"hvy":true,"kno":true,"kee":false,"lgt":false,"lng":false,"mel":true,"mgc":false,"nim":false,"one":false,"pen":false,"pun":false,"rng":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"sta":false,"sun":false,"thr":false,"trp":true,"two":true,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MQavDY2ZxPthZn3c":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663965793448,"modifiedTime":1664215304115,"lastModifiedBy":"MQavDY2ZxPthZn3c"},"_id":"f76rjxnhOlJjbpWT"}
{"name":"Poleaxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-engraved-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An infantry weapon designed for use against armored foes, characterized by an axe on one side and a hammer on the other, tipped with a dagger-like spike from the top. It is typically on a 6 ft haft, shod with iron to protect it from damage. Though not long enough for a reach weapon, its style resembles that of a quarterstaff and axe combined. A master uses the weapon's iron shodding more actively, blocking attacks that would normally chop through the wood shaft.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"RME","quantity":1,"weight":7,"price":40,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d10+@mod",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"axes","baseItem":"poleaxe","properties":{"unt":false,"bsc":true,"mst":false,"aff":false,"amm":false,"awk":false,"bar":false,"bal":false,"bra":true,"con":false,"def":true,"dis":false,"dbl":false,"ent":false,"fir":false,"fin":false,"hip":false,"hvy":true,"kno":false,"kee":false,"lgt":false,"lng":false,"mel":true,"mgc":false,"nim":false,"one":false,"pen":true,"pun":true,"rng":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"sta":true,"sun":false,"thr":false,"trp":true,"two":true,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MQavDY2ZxPthZn3c":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","co